    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Wait, what do you mean by the goblins' ability to absorb gold? I was just asking about B12 and intrinsic factor. Can we stick to the biochemistry? I'm specifically trying to understand the step-by-step process from the mouth to the ileum.",
      "source": "evaluator",
